	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My interpretation is that the samples were streamed to the SPC700 and then outputted that way (AKA, they're BRR samples). SPC dumps would get the vocal samples wrong in this fashion.<br /><br />I know this because I played Soreyuke Ebisumaru Karakuri Meiro Kieta Goemon no Nazo (also by Konami) and I realized the vocal samples were streamed after doing some SPC dumps.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
